casebody.data:
Mentor Lumber and Supply Company, Appellant, v. Victor, d.b.a. Johnnycake Homes; Victor, Appellee.

[Cite as Mentor Lumber & Supply Co. v. Victor (1993), 67 Ohio St.3d 1202.]

(No. 92-1065 Submitted May 19, 1993 Decided July 28, 1993.) Dworken & Bernstein Co., L.P.A., and Patrick J. Perotti, for appellant. Cannon, Stem, Aveni & Loiacono Co., L.P.A., and Timothy P. Cannon, for appellee Ralph Victor.

The appeal is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently allowed.

*1203A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Resnick and F.E. Sweeney, JJ., concur. Moyer, C.J., and Wright, J., dissent. Pfeifer, J., dissents and would affirm.
